info:
  program: xun
  args:
    - "--help"
---
success: true
exit_code: 0
----- stdout -----
xun - bookmark + proxy CLI

Usage: xun.exe [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  bookmark    Bookmark management and navigation
  proxy       Proxy management
  backup      Incremental project backup
  env         Environment variable management
  acl         Windows ACL management
  config      Manage ~/.xun.config.json
  ctx         Context switch profiles
  tree        Generate directory tree
  find        Find files and directories by pattern and metadata
  video       Video operations
  port        Port management
  proc        Process management
  rm          Force delete files or delete bookmarks with --bookmark (-bm)
  fs-rm       Delete a file or directory
  init        Initialize shell integration (print wrapper function)
  completion  Generate shell completion script
  help        Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --no-color         disable ANSI colors (or set NO_COLOR=1)
  -q, --quiet            suppress UI output
  -v, --verbose          verbose output
      --non-interactive  force non-interactive mode
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format [default: auto] [possible values: auto, table, json, tsv,
                         csv]
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version

----- stderr -----
